headline: The Ultimate Oil Stock to Buy With $200 Right Now
summary: Warren Buffet has one of the best investing track records of all time.  If you want to find profitable investments, just pay attention to Buffett's portfolio.  In fact, it's possible that Buffett will eventually buy the entire company.

headline: Occidental: Foggy Outlook And Overvaluation
